全球确诊病例超28万！意大利病毒传播或早于中国疫情暴发。
There are more than 280,000 confirmed cases in the world! The spread of the Italian virus predates or predates the outbreak in China.
中国经营报                      。
China Business News.
中国经营报。
China Business News.
与中国企业同步成长，对话商业领袖，传播商业理想，服务商业人群，《中国经营报》掌控中国商界绝对话语权。
Growing in step with Chinese companies, dialogue with business leaders, spreading business ideals, serving the business community, The China Business Administration controls the absolute voice of the Chinese business community.
。
.
综合报道，据美国约翰斯·霍普金斯大学发布的实时统计数据显示，截至美国东部时间21日9时13分(北京时间21日21时13分)，全球新冠肺炎确诊病例累计达284566例，死亡病例达11868例。
At 9: 13 a.m. EDT (21: 13 a.m. Beijing time), 28,4566 new cases of pneumonia and 11,868 deaths had been confirmed worldwide, according to real-time statistics released by Johns Hopkins University.
其中，中国以外，意大利、西班牙、伊朗和德国四国确诊病例超2万；意大利专家称，该国病毒传播或早于中国疫情暴发；非洲疫情已蔓延至40个国家，确诊病例过千。
Outside China, more than 20,000 cases have been confirmed in Italy, Spain, Iran and Germany; Italian experts say the virus may have spread earlier than the outbreak in China; and the epidemic in Africa has spread to 40 countries, with more than 1,000 confirmed cases.
近日来，又有多艘邮轮上的乘客确诊，全球邮轮业大范围停航。
In recent days, passengers on a number of cruise ships have confirmed that the global cruise industry has been largely discontinued.
意大利威尼斯，工作人员在公共区域内喷洒消毒剂。
Workers spray disinfectant on public areas in Venice, Italy.
中国以外四国确诊病例超2万专家：意大利病毒传播或早于中国疫情暴发　　截至当地时间20日下午6时，意大利新冠肺炎确诊病例增至47021例，累计死亡4032例。
Four countries outside China confirmed cases more than 20,000 experts: Italy virus spread or before the outbreak of the Chinese outbreak as of 6 p.m. local time, Italy's new crown pneumonia confirmed cases increased to 47,021 cases, a cumulative total of 4,032 deaths.
伦巴第大区主席阿迪里奥·丰塔纳举行记者会表示，中央政府已批准在伦巴第大区境内部署军队，执行封城命令。
The President of the Lombardy region, Adirio Fontana, told a press conference that the central Government had approved the deployment of troops in the Lombardy region to enforce the closure order.
意大利马里奥·内格里药理学研究所负责人朱塞佩·雷穆齐教授日前在接受美国媒体采访时表示，新冠病毒可能早于新冠疫情在中国暴发前，就已在意大利传播。
Professor Giuseppe Remucci, director of the Mario Negri Institute of Pharmacology in Italy, said in an interview with US media that the virus could have spread in Italy before the outbreak of the new crown.
在被美国全国公共广播电台(NPR)问及意大利为何在2月21日疫情暴发后表现得措手不及时，雷穆齐表示，他从全科医生们那里获悉，早在去年12月甚至11月的时候，他们就记得见到过一种“非常陌生且极为严重的不明原因肺炎”，特别是在老年人身上。
Asked by US National Public Radio why Italy was caught off guard after the February 21 outbreak, Mr Remucci said he had heard from general practitioners that they had seen "a very strange and very serious case of unexplained pneumonia" as early as December or even November last year, especially among the elderly.
“这意味着在我们注意到疫情在中国暴发以前，这种病毒就已经在意大利传播了，至少在北部伦巴第大区是如此。
"This means that the virus spread in Italy, at least in the northern Lombardy region, before we noticed an outbreak in China.
”　　此外，伊朗卫生部21日宣布，伊朗新增新冠肺炎确诊病例966例，累计确诊20610例，其中1556例死亡，治愈7635例。
In addition, Iran's Ministry of Health announced Tuesday 966 new cases of confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in Iran, with a cumulative total of 20,610 confirmed cases, including 1,556 deaths and 7,635 cured.
伊朗总统鲁哈尼表示，伊朗为抗击新冠肺炎疫情，采取了包括旅行限制等在内的社交疏离措施，这些措施将持续两到三周的时间，因为他预计届时该国疫情可能会得到缓解。
Iranian President Hassan Rouhani says Iran has taken social isolation measures, including travel restrictions, to fight the outbreak, which will last two to three weeks as he expects the epidemic to ease.
据德国媒体NTV21日报道的最新数据，德国新冠肺炎累计确诊病例已超过2万例。
A cumulative total of more than 20,000 cases of pneumonia have been confirmed in Germany, according to the latest figures reported by the German media, NTV21.
目前，德国已实施关闭学校、公共设施、餐馆酒吧等严格的防疫措施。
At present, Germany has implemented the closure of schools, public facilities, restaurants and bars and other stringent preventive measures.
西班牙卫生部21日公布，该国新冠肺炎累计确诊病例达24926例，单日新增近5000例。
A total of 24,926 cases of pneumonia have been confirmed in Spain, with nearly 5,000 new cases reported in a single day, the Health Ministry said on Monday.
为应对床位不足的情况，西班牙军队已开始在奥维耶多、希洪等地搭建帐篷医院。
In response to the shortage of beds, the Spanish army has begun to build tent hospitals in Oviedo, Chihoun and other places.
非洲40国出现确诊病例经济和旅游业受冲击　　随着安哥拉报告发现新冠肺炎病例，截至北京时间3月21日17时30分，非洲大陆已有40个国家确诊出现新冠肺炎病例，总数为1003例，其中包括25例死亡，104例治愈。
Confirmed Cases in 40 African Countries Attack on Economy and Tourism With Angola reporting new cases of pneumonia, 40 countries on the continent had confirmed new cases of pneumonia by 17: 30 March Beijing time, bringing the total to 1,003, including 25 deaths and 104 cures.
目前，撒哈拉以南非洲确诊病例数前三位的国家仍是南非、塞内加尔和布基纳法索，这3个国家和加纳、尼日利亚、喀麦隆等国都已出现本地传播病例，引发医卫专家对疫情可能在部分国家暴发的担忧。
Currently, the top three countries in sub-Saharan Africa continue to be South Africa, Senegal and Burkina Faso, all of which, along with countries such as Ghana, Nigeria and Cameroon, have already experienced local transmission, raising concerns among health experts about the possibility of outbreaks in some countries.
一些国家采取措施防控境外输入性病例。
Some countries have taken measures to prevent and control imported cases abroad.
尼日利亚关闭3个州的国际机场；塞内加尔暂停所有国际航班；几内亚取消所有来自疫情严重国家的航班；加蓬关闭陆海空边境并取消所有国内外航班；乌干达、博茨瓦纳等国限制疫情高风险国家人员入境；南非航空停飞所有国际航线至5月底；非洲最大的航空公司——埃塞俄比亚航空暂停飞往约30个国家的航班。
Nigeria closed international airports in three states; Senegal suspended all international flights; Guinea cancelled all flights from highly affected countries; Gabon closed its land, sea and air borders and cancelled all domestic and international flights; countries such as Uganda and Botswana restricted the entry of persons from high-risk countries; South African Airlines suspended all international flights until the end of May; and Ethiopian Airlines, Africa's largest airline, suspended flights to some 30 countries.
疫情的不断扩散，对非洲的经济和旅游业造成冲击。
The continuing spread of the epidemic is having an impact on Africa's economy and tourism.
联合国非洲经济委员会发布报告认为，2020年非洲经济增速可能从此前预期的3.2%降至1.8%。
The report released by the United Nations Economic Commission for Africa says growth in Africa is likely to slow to 1.8 percent in 2020 from 3.2 percent.
此外，津巴布韦和纳米比亚2月以来的旅游订单分别减少70%和30%，坦桑尼亚旅游胜地桑给巴尔岛95%的酒店也已停业。
In addition, tourist orders in Zimbabwe and Namibia have declined by 70 per cent and 30 per cent, respectively, since February, and 95 per cent of hotels in the Tanzanian resort island of Zanzibar have been closed.
3月20日，韩国仁川国际机场，海报上印有“禁止运出口罩”字样。
March 20, Incheon International Airport, South Korea, the poster printed with the words "No Exit Mask."
韩国政府称，22日起将要求持长期签证的欧洲入境者进行14天隔离。
The South Korean government said it would require long-term visa holders to be quarantined for 14 days from now.
中新社记者 曾鼐 摄　　韩国单日新增病例再次增至三位数澳大利亚确诊逾千人　　在亚洲，韩国境内单日新增病例再次增至三位数；日本现集体感染事件；菲律宾新增病例创单日最大增幅；澳大利亚确诊病例已超过千人……　　韩国中央防疫对策本部21日通报，截至当天0时，韩国较前一天0时新增147例感染新型冠状病毒(COVID-19)确诊病例，累计确诊8799例。
Chinese news agency reporters Zeng Nai single-day new cases in South Korea again to three digits in Asia, South Korea now collective infections in Japan, the largest increase in the Philippines in a day, more than 1,000 confirmed cases in Australia...
韩国中央灾难安全本部表示，为了防止疫情从境外输入，政府将安排1000间规模的临时生活设施，专供从欧洲入境人员接受隔离。
South Korea's Central Disaster Safety Ministry said the government will arrange 1,000 temporary living facilities for people coming from Europe to be quarantined to prevent the disease from being imported from abroad.
3月21日，日本大分县知事广濑胜贞在记者会上表示，在当地医院发生新冠肺炎集体感染事件。
On March 21, Japanese governor Guangse Setoyama told a news conference that there had been a mass infection with pneumonia in the local hospital.
据介绍，在国立医院机构大分医疗中心，包括医生、护士以及已经转院的患者在内共计5人感染新冠肺炎。
A total of five people, including doctors, nurses and patients who had already been transferred to hospital, were newly infected with pneumonia, according to the report.
目前该医疗机构已经暂停门诊，并分批对医务人员和住院患者共600余人进行新冠病毒检测。
At present, the clinic has been suspended and more than 600 medical staff and inpatients have been tested for the new crown virus in batches.
当地时间21日下午，菲律宾报告新增77例新冠肺炎病例，系单日最大增幅，该国感染病例总数累计达307例，死亡人数为19人。
On the afternoon of May 21, the Philippines reported 77 new cases of New Crown Pneumonia, the largest single-day increase, with a cumulative total of 307 cases and 19 deaths in the country.
为降低传染率，菲律宾总统杜特尔特下令将吕宋岛封锁一个月，并对居民实施了限制性隔离措施。
To reduce the rate of infection, Philippine President Narendra Dutert ordered a one-month blockade of Luzon and imposed a restrictive quarantine on residents.
杜特尔特还要求学校关闭、禁止大规模集会、暂停公共交通。
He also called for schools to be closed, mass rallies banned and public transport suspended.
泰国公共卫生部21日发布公告称，泰国新增89例新冠肺炎确诊病例，累计确诊病例数达到411例。
Thailand's Ministry of Public Health announced on Monday that 89 new cases of pneumonia have been confirmed in Thailand, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 411.
与此同时，泰国多府宣布关闭大部分陆路边境关卡。
At the same time, Thailand announced the closure of most land border posts.
澳大利亚新冠病毒感染病例也在持续上升，目前已超过千人。
Australia also continues to see an increase in new crown virus infections, which now number more than a thousand.
澳总理莫里森20日再次呼吁每一个澳人贡献自己的一份力量，保持社交距离。
Australian Prime Minister Morrison 20 again called on each and every Australian to contribute their share to maintain a social distance.
多艘邮轮乘客确诊全球邮轮业大范围停航　　随着疫情的不断扩散，欧洲最大邮轮公司意大利歌诗达邮轮此前宣布，将在4月3日前暂停全球范围所有航线的运营。
Many Cruise Passengers Confirmed Global Cruise Lines With the spread of the epidemic, Italy's largest cruise line, Comesta, announced it would suspend operations on all routes around the world until April 3.
此外，世界几大邮轮公司，包括歌诗达的母公司嘉年华集团，皇家加勒比邮轮公司等纷纷宣布，由于新冠病毒的暴发，他们暂停了在全球或部分地区的运营。
In addition, some of the world's biggest cruise companies, including Goethea's parent, Carnival Group and Royal Caribbean Cruises, have announced that they have suspended operations around the world or parts of the world because of the outbreak of the new Crown virus.
20日，法国马赛官员表示，一艘载有千人的意大利邮轮“歌诗达耀目”号在该国南部港口马赛港停靠，船上逾600名乘客将下船。
More than 600 passengers will disembark on board an Italian cruise ship carrying 1,000 people at the southern port of Marseille, French officials said Tuesday.
此前，该邮轮上已被证实有36名乘客确诊患新冠肺炎。
The vessel had been confirmed to have 36 passengers diagnosed with pneumonia.
而之前停靠在悉尼的“红宝石公主”号邮轮，乘客中有3人新冠病毒检测呈阳性。
Three of the passengers aboard the previous cruise ship, Princess Ruby, which docked in Sydney, tested positive for the virus.
值得注意的是，此前该船上约2700名乘客都已下船回家。
It is worth noting that some 2,700 passengers from the vessel had already disembarked and returned home.
新南威尔士州卫生局紧急联系所有乘客，告知这一消息，并要求他们自我隔离14天。
The NSW Health Authority immediately contacted all passengers to inform them of this information and required them to remain in isolation for 14 days.
18日，载有至少6名新冠肺炎患者的“布雷马”号邮轮停靠古巴港口，船上大部分人当晚搭包机返回英国。
On the 18th, the MV Braima, carrying at least six people with pneumonia, docked at a Cuban port, and most of the crew returned to Britain on chartered flights that night.
据了解，“布雷马”号邮轮属于英国弗雷德·奥尔森航运公司，载有超过1000名乘客和船员，乘客主要为英国人。
It is understood that the MV Braima belonged to the British shipping company Fred Olsen and carried more than 1,000 passengers and crew, mainly British.
该邮轮此前因出现新冠肺炎疫情，在加勒比地区多国港口申请靠岸遭拒。
The cruise ship had been denied landing in a Caribbean multi-country port due to the outbreak of new crown pneumonia.
古巴政府16日宣布允许该邮轮停靠本国港口。
The Cuban government on the 16th announced that the ship allowed to call at its port.
据美国有线电视新闻网(CNN)21日报道，如今，有30多艘邮轮仍在海上，搭载着数千名乘客。
More than 30 cruise ships are still at sea carrying thousands of passengers, CNN reported Thursday.
在全球邮轮行业停滞、人们对疫情越来越担忧的情况下，这些邮轮试图寻找港口停靠。
With the global cruise industry at a standstill and growing concerns about the outbreak, these ships are trying to find ports to call at.
